strong, with the gaping holes on the light squares Black is in desperate
trouble.[%csl Gc2][%cal Ra3c3]} (29. Qxc4 $2 Qd5 $1 $11) 29... Qe7 ({Moreover,
Black can't hold the Pd4, as the tactical} 29... Rb2 {fails to} 30. Rxc3 Qa5
31. Qh7+ Kf7 32. Re5 $1 Qxc3 33. Rg5 $18) (29... Rb7 30. Rxc3 Qa5 31. Qh7+ Kf7
